'''约翰·布赖森'''（{{lang-en|John Edgar Bryson}}，{{bd|1943年|7月24日||}}）<ref>[http://www.referenceforbusiness.com/biography/A-E/Bryson-John-E-1943.html John E. Bryson 1943-] {{Wayback|url=http://www.referenceforbusiness.com/biography/A-E/Bryson-John-E-1943.html |date=20200807041927 }}, ''Reference for Business', Encyclopedia of Business 2nd edition</ref>是第37任[[美国商务部长|美国商务部长]]。他以前是{{tsl|en|Edison International|}}公司的主席、首席执行官和总裁。

== 早年与教育 ==
1961年他毕业于[[波特蘭_(俄勒岡州)|波特兰]]的 ''Cleveland High School'' <ref>{{cite news|last=Pope|first=Charles|title=John Bryson brings Portland roots as nominee to lead Commerce Department|url=http://www.oregonlive.com/politics/index.ssf/2011/05/john_bryson_brings_portland_ro.html|accessdate=31 May 2011|newspaper=The Oregonian|date=May 31, 2011|archive-date=2018-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613040932/http://www.oregonlive.com/politics/index.ssf/2011/05/john_bryson_brings_portland_ro.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1965年获得[[斯坦福大学|斯坦福大学]]的学士学位，1969年获得[[耶鲁大学|耶鲁大学]][[耶鲁法学院|法学院]]的[[法律博士|法律博士]]。

== 职业 ==
1970年他与其他几名耶鲁大学法学院的毕业生一起创建了{{Link-en|自然資源保護委員會|Natural Resources Defense Council}}，并担任该组织的法律顾问<ref>[http://articles.latimes.com/1990-10-01/news/mn-1223_1_natural-resources-defense-council Ex-Environment Activist Will Take Helm at Edison] {{Wayback|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1990-10-01/news/mn-1223_1_natural-resources-defense-council |date=20121107020453 }}, Larry B. Stammer, Michael Parrish, Times staff writers, ''[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]'', October 1, 1990</ref><ref>[http://www.anderson.ucla.edu/x14873.xml Edison International Chairman John E. Bryson to Deliver UCLA Anderson Commencement Address, June 16] {{Wayback|url=http://www.anderson.ucla.edu/x14873.xml |date=20111221050225 }}, [[安德森管理学院|安德森管理学院]], May 16, 2006</ref>。

1976-79年，他担任{{Link-en|加州水資源控制委員會|California State Water Resources Control Board}}主席；1979-82年，他担任{{Link-en|加州公用事业委员会|California Public Utilities Commission}}主席。

从1990年到2008年7月31日，他一直担任Edison International的总裁，之后由Ted Craver接替他<ref>[http://www.edison.com/ourcompany/management.asp?id=1836 John E. Bryson] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060314001842/http://www.edison.com/ourcompany/management.asp?id=1836 |date=2006-03-14 }}, {{tsl|en|Edison (company)||Edison International}}</ref>。

他是[[波音公司|波音公司]]、{{tsl|en|W. M. Keck Foundation|}}和[[华特迪士尼公司|华特迪士尼公司]]的[[董事|董事]]。此外，他也曾在许多教育、环保和其他公益的组织效力，比如担任California Business Roundtable主席、[[斯坦福大学|斯坦福大学]]董事、[[加州理工学院|加州理工学院]]董事、Pacific Council on International Policy联合主席之一和Public Policy Institute of California主席<ref>[http://investing.businessweek.com/businessweek/research/stocks/people/person.asp?personId=301893&ticker=KKR:US&previousCapId=410467&previousTitle=DEUTSCHE%20BANK%20AG-REGISTERED John E. Bryson], ''[[彭博商业周刊|彭博商业周刊]]''</ref><ref>[http://www.ppic.org/main/bio.asp?i=411 John E. Bryson] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110814044816/http://www.ppic.org/main/bio.asp?i=411 |date=2011-08-14 }}, {{tsl|en|Public Policy Institute of California|}}</ref>。

=== 商务部长 ===
2011年5月31日，[[奥巴马|奥巴马]]提名布赖森为商务部长人选，以接替将任[[美國驻华大使|美國驻华大使]]的[[骆家辉|骆家辉]]<ref>[http://whitehouse.blogs.cnn.com/2011/05/31/obama-makes-it-official/ Obama makes it official] {{Wayback|url=http://whitehouse.blogs.cnn.com/2011/05/31/obama-makes-it-official/ |date=20210325233121 }}, Alexander Mooney, [[CNN|CNN]]'', May 31, 2011</ref>。2011年10月20日，[[美国参议院|美国参议院]]以74票赞成26反对的结果通过这一任命<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.senate.gov/galleries/pdcl/index.htm |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-03-07  |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111126173242/http://www.senate.gov/galleries/pdcl/index.htm |archivedate=2011-11-26 }}</ref>，10月21日正式上任<ref>[http://www.commerce.gov/news/press-releases/2011/10/21/john-bryson-sworn-37th-secretary-commerce {{Wayback|url=http://www.commerce.gov/news/press-releases/2011/10/21/john-bryson-sworn-37th-secretary-commerce |date=20131231000245 }} Press Release, John Bryson Sworn In as 37th Secretary of Commerce</ref>。

